---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="About — HyperLog">
  <Header />

  <main class="flex-grow pt-24">

    <!-- Logo -->
    <section class="pt-6 pb-12 px-6 flex justify-center bg-surface-base">
      <img src="/logo/logo-full-on-dark.svg" alt="HyperLog" class="w-[250px] md:w-[300px]" />
    </section>

    <!-- ============================================================
         COMPANY STORY
         ============================================================ -->
    <section class="py-16 px-6 bg-surface-base relative overflow-hidden">
      <div class="absolute inset-0 z-0">
        <img src="/images/newyork.jpeg" alt="" class="w-full h-full object-cover brightness-[0.55] saturate-90" style="object-position: center 40%;" />
        <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-surface-base/40"></div>
      </div>
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto relative z-10">
        <p class="section-label text-secondary mb-4">Our Story</p>
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-8 tracking-tight">Aviation Meets Blockchain</h2>

        <div class="space-y-6 text-secondary text-base leading-relaxed">
          <p>
            JetLink Technologies was founded by aviation and technology professionals to modernise the operational infrastructure the aviation industry depends on. Our platforms span blockchain-secured records, AI-driven analytics, real-time fleet management, and digital credential systems — and are already deployed in active operations.
          </p>
          <div class="flex justify-center py-2"><span class="text-outline/20">— — —</span></div>
          <p>
            The pilot licensing and logbook system has barely changed in decades. Records are paper-based, fragmented across airlines and authorities, and unverifiable. Pilots spend hours calculating hour breakdowns for job applications. Regulators have no mechanism to digitally verify credentials. Ramp inspectors rely on physical documents and trust.
          </p>
          <div class="flex justify-center py-2"><span class="text-outline/20">— — —</span></div>
          <p>
            HyperLog exists because we live this problem every day. Built by a Boeing 767 First Officer and an engineer, it is the system we wished existed — a blockchain logbook with multi-source verification, and ICAO-aligned digital credentials that can be verified offline, anywhere in the world.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ============================================================
         FOUNDERS
         ============================================================ -->
    <section class="py-16 px-6 bg-surface-lowest">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <p class="section-label text-secondary mb-4">Leadership</p>
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-4 tracking-tight">Founded by Operators</h2>
        <p class="text-secondary text-base leading-relaxed mb-12 max-w-2xl">
          Christian and Vincent are both active airline pilots and experienced software engineers who have worked together since the development of FlightFile, a flight planning tool used by Norwegian Airlines pilots. With 40 years of combined aviation experience and 20 years of collective software engineering knowledge, they bring frontline operational insight and a shared conviction that aviation deserves better infrastructure.
        </p>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
          <!-- Christian -->
          <div class="bg-surface-container rounded-xl ghost-border p-8">
            <img src="/christian-charalambous.jpg" alt="Christian Charalambous" class="w-20 h-20 rounded-full object-cover border-2 border-primary/20 mb-6" />
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-1">Christian Charalambous</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-primary font-semibold mb-4">CEO & Co-Founder</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-secondary leading-relaxed mb-4">
              Boeing 767 pilot and seasoned aviation professional with a First Class Honours degree in Air Transport Operations. Brings global operational experience across cargo and passenger airlines, combined with four years leading a consultancy specialising in Web3, IoT, and AI.
            </p>
            <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/christiancharalambous/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-xs text-primary hover:text-white transition-colors">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M20.447 20.452h-3.554v-5.569c0-1.328-.027-3.037-1.852-3.037-1.853 0-2.136 1.445-2.136 2.939v5.667H9.351V9h3.414v1.561h.046c.477-.9 1.637-1.85 3.37-1.85 3.601 0 4.267 2.37 4.267 5.455v6.286zM5.337 7.433c-1.144 0-2.063-.926-2.063-2.065 0-1.138.92-2.063 2.063-2.063 1.14 0 2.064.925 2.064 2.063 0 1.139-.925 2.065-2.064 2.065zm1.782 13.019H3.555V9h3.564v11.452zM22.225 0H1.771C.792 0 0 .774 0 1.729v20.542C0 23.227.792 24 1.771 24h20.451C23.2 24 24 23.227 24 22.271V1.729C24 .774 23.2 0 22.222 0h.003z"/></svg>
              LinkedIn
            </a>
          </div>

          <!-- Vincent -->
          <div class="bg-surface-container rounded-xl ghost-border p-8">
            <img src="/vincent-malterre.jpg" alt="Vincent Malterre" class="w-20 h-20 rounded-full object-cover border-2 border-primary/20 mb-6" />
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-1">Vincent Malterre</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-primary font-semibold mb-4">CTO & Co-Founder</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-secondary leading-relaxed mb-4">
              Boeing 737 pilot with extensive European airline experience and the creator of FlightFile, adopted by over 500 pilots. Brings a decade of software engineering expertise alongside a background running a French textile company.
            </p>
            <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/vincent-malterre-805845124/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-xs text-primary hover:text-white transition-colors">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M20.447 20.452h-3.554v-5.569c0-1.328-.027-3.037-1.852-3.037-1.853 0-2.136 1.445-2.136 2.939v5.667H9.351V9h3.414v1.561h.046c.477-.9 1.637-1.85 3.37-1.85 3.601 0 4.267 2.37 4.267 5.455v6.286zM5.337 7.433c-1.144 0-2.063-.926-2.063-2.065 0-1.138.92-2.063 2.063-2.063 1.14 0 2.064.925 2.064 2.063 0 1.139-.925 2.065-2.064 2.065zm1.782 13.019H3.555V9h3.564v11.452zM22.225 0H1.771C.792 0 0 .774 0 1.729v20.542C0 23.227.792 24 1.771 24h20.451C23.2 24 24 23.227 24 22.271V1.729C24 .774 23.2 0 22.222 0h.003z"/></svg>
              LinkedIn
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ============================================================
         MISSION & VALUES
         ============================================================ -->
    <section class="py-16 px-6 bg-surface-lowest">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 mb-16">
          <div>
            <p class="section-label text-primary mb-4">Mission</p>
            <p class="text-lg text-white font-semibold leading-relaxed">
              To provide aviation professionals with modern, intelligent, and secure operational infrastructure — engineered by professionals who understand the industry from the inside.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <p class="section-label text-primary mb-4">Vision</p>
            <p class="text-lg text-white font-semibold leading-relaxed">
              An aviation industry where every pilot's credentials are digitally verifiable, every flight hour is immutably recorded, and trust is built into the infrastructure — not assumed.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-4">
          <div class="bg-surface-container rounded-lg ghost-border p-6">
            <h4 class="text-sm font-bold text-white mb-2">Operational Truth</h4>
            <p class="text-xs text-secondary leading-relaxed">Every solution is built for the reality of aviation operations, not the theory.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-surface-container rounded-lg ghost-border p-6">
            <h4 class="text-sm font-bold text-white mb-2">Security First</h4>
            <p class="text-xs text-secondary leading-relaxed">Blockchain-secured, encrypted, and fully auditable. Pilot data remains under pilot control.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-surface-container rounded-lg ghost-border p-6">
            <h4 class="text-sm font-bold text-white mb-2">Technical Excellence</h4>
            <p class="text-xs text-secondary leading-relaxed">Modern architecture, rigorous engineering standards, and systems designed to scale.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-surface-container rounded-lg ghost-border p-6">
            <h4 class="text-sm font-bold text-white mb-2">Partnership</h4>
            <p class="text-xs text-secondary leading-relaxed">We integrate directly with your operation. Your challenges become our priorities.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

  </main>

  <Footer />
</BaseLayout>
